    <h1>Game Rules</h1>
    <h2>General Rules</h2>
    <p>Hearthstone Battlegrounds has 60 bosses and 143 minions in total. Before each game, each player can select one of the four bosses provided, and each boss has its own hero power. The Tier List of the heroes is provided in the later section.</p>
    <p>There are 8 players in each game, and each player has 40 health(except Patchwerk, who has 55 health due to its hero power). Players end their game when their bosses have 0 or negative health, and the game is ranked based on the time they knock out.</p>
    <p>There are 2 phases for each round: Recruit Phase and Combat Phase.
    <h2>Recruit Phase</h2>
    <p>During recruit phase, each player has certain amount of coins (between 3 and 10), and players are allowed to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li> use 3 coins to recruit a minion from the Tavern</li>
      <li> get 1 coin by selling a minion</li>
      <li> use 1 coin to refresh all minions in the current Tavern</li>
      <li> freeze the Tavern and recruit minions in the next round
      <li> freely rearrange the minions owned</li>
      <li> automatically fuse 3 identical cards to a triple card and obtain a card from the Tavern Tier above(or from Tier 6 if players are at Tier 6)</li>
