    <h2>Combat Phase</h2>
    <p>In the Combat Phase, each player enters combat with another player, facing off against their board. At the end of combad, the player with surviving minions deals damage to their opponents. The damage is the Tavern tier + the combined tiers of all surviving minions.

    <p>For more details, please visit <a href="https://playhearthstone.com/en-us/news/23156373">HearthStone Batteground Official Rules.</a></p>

